@{b}The Movie & Series Pilot@{ub}

The roots of Buffy The Vampire Slayer - recommended viewing for genuine obsessives.

MOVIE		@{" Buffy The Vampire Slayer (Movie) " LINK "BUFFYTHEMOVIE"}
PILOT		@{" Buffy The Vampire Slayer (Pilot) " LINK "PILOT"}


@{b}Season One Episodes@{ub}

This, along with the second season, is the golden age of Buffy the Vampire Slayer. The season was roughly half as long as the following seasons, which added to the pace. Far be it from me to suggest that this season was entirely perfect, but there's something about it that seems really fresh and youthful. It could be the lower budget, the influence of different writers, or just how young the actors look - it was 6 years ago, after all. Saving the world is pretty every-day stuff in Buffy these days but at the end of season one, seeing it for the first time, it was a big deal.

