@{b}Season Two Episodes@{ub}

I think everyone who has ever seen a television set has probably seen an episode from this season. Think season two, think Buffy and Angel. Their love story is the backbone of this season, and the influence of it seeps into almost every new Buffy episode - not to mention the Angel series. This really is @{i}the @{ui} classic season and finishes in total cliff-hanger mode: something none of the other seasons really do.

