@{b}Season Three Episodes@{ub}

The first season to show signs of the psychological darkness and maturity of seasons 5 and 6, season three is also notable because it marks the Scooby Gang's last year in high school. Faith appears and rapidly develops into a fascinating and dangerous character. The whole show takes on another dimension, 'The Wish' being most indicative of the studio's newfound willingness to experiment with the Buffy formula.

