@{b}Season Six Episodes@{ub}

Season six might as well be an extension of season five - dealing with the aftermath of everything that went on, not least Buffy's death. This season has easily the most disturbing moment the show has ever seen - Spike's attempt to rape Buffy. Also because Buffy was dead, there was much speculation about whether this season would materialise. Bringing her back would prove hard for Joss & co to pull off while satisfying the fans, and some would rather the show went out with a bang, than being reduced to a kludge like The X-Files has since David Duchovny lost interest. It manages, however, to kick arse in time-honoured fashion.

