Clement - Clem to his friends - is a lovable, loose-skinned demon who hung out with Spike for a while until he disappeared, leaving Clem to look after his crypt. Entertained Dawn with a Nachos taste-tester during @{"Two To Go" LINK "TWOTOGO"} while Anya, Buffy and Xander looked for Willow, who was hellbent on vegeance over the Trio after Warren shot Tara.

