@node "ABOUTDREG" "Buffy.guide: About Dreg"

@{b}Dreg@{ub}
()

Servant to Glory, Dreg would bring humans to Glory's hideout for her to feed on. He also helped her obtain age-old spells to help her find the key and had an annoying habbit of calling her "oh naughty-feelings-inspiring Glorifficus" and such-like.

@{b}Goto:@{ub}   @{" String Search " SYSTEM "newcli WINDOW=CON:20/20/400//Buffy from Buffy.guide.cli"}@{"?" LINK "SEARCHREADME"}  @{" Major Events " LINK "EVENTS"}  @{" Characters " LINK "CHARACTERPROFILES"}  @{" Vocabulary " LINK "VAMPVOC"}  @{" Main Page " LINK "MAIN"}
