@node "ABOUTMRTRICK" "Buffy.guide: About Mr. Trick"

@{b}Mr. Trick@{ub}

1999, first appears in @{"Faith, Hope and Trick" LINK "FAITHHOPETRICK"}.

This elusive and sardonic vampire constantly schemed to destroy Buffy. He arrived in Sunnydale with Kakistos, with whom he began his unrelenting quest to kill the slayer and take over the town. He worked closely with the Mayor after his failed Slayerfest '98, and although he usually employed others to hunt Buffy down, he wasn't afraid to go toe-to-toe with her himself.

