@node "ABOUTMOUTHLESSDEMON" "Buffy.guide: About Mouthless Demon"

@{b}Mouthless Demon@{ub}

Featured in @{"Earshot" LINK "EARSHOT"}.

When Buffy killed one of these mouthless demons, she inadvertently absorbed some of their fluorescent blood, she gained their power of telepathy. In order to cure her of this curse, Angel brought her a concoction containing the heart of one of the demons, which returned her senses to normal.

@{b}Goto:@{ub}   @{" String Search " SYSTEM "newcli WINDOW=CON:20/20/400//Buffy from Buffy.guide.cli"}@{"?" LINK "SEARCHREADME"}  @{" Major Events " LINK "EVENTS"}  @{" Characters " LINK "CHARACTERPROFILES"}  @{" Vocabulary " LINK "VAMPVOC"}  @{" Main Page " LINK "MAIN"}
