@node "ABOUTMUSICDEMON" "Buffy.guide: About Music Demon"

@{b}Music Demon@{ub}
()

Appears in @{"Once More, With Feeling" LINK "ONCEMOREWITHFEELING"}.

Summoned by @{"Xander" LINK "ABOUTXANDER"}, who hoped the demon's powers of song would help the gang reach a "happy ending", Music Demon (whose proper name was never revealed) had the whole town singing about parking tickets and mustard stains, that is before they danced so fast they burst into flames. Crucially, the singing and dancing got out-of-control enough to lead to the leaking of several secrets among the gang. The demon attempts to make Dawn his bride, believing she summoned him, but when he learns it was Xander, he decides to give it a miss and says goodbye.

