@{b}Olaf the Troll@{ub}

Appears in @{"Triangle" LINK "TRIANGLE"}.

Summoned accidentally when Willow and Anya have an argument mid-spell, Olaf goes on a wrecking spree through Sunnydale threatening to "make merry" with the town's virgins and eat babies. One wonders. Olaf used to date Anya - in fact he was her first victim, the reason she became a vengeance demon. Buffy later uses Olaf's hammer to beat Glory to a bloody pulp.

