@node "ABOUTOVUMOBANI" "Buffy.guide: About Ovu Mobani (Pat)"

@{b}Ovu Mobani (Pat)@{ub}
()

Appears in @{"Dead Man's Party" LINK "DEADMANSPARTY"}.

When Joyce Summers purchased an ancient Nigerian mask, she had no idea that it housed the zombie demon Ovu Mobani. The mask has the power to awaken the dead who wreak havoc on Sunnydale, and turn its wearer (Joyce's zombified friend Pat) into the demon incarnate. The only way to destroy it is to puncture its glowing, red eyes.

