()

Appears in @{"Beauty And The Beasts" LINK "BEAUTYANDBEASTS"}.

After overdosing on a potion he created to increase his testosterone level, Pete transforms into a marauding monster whenever he gets angry. With veins bulging, his victims are guys who he thinks are after his girlfriend, Debbie, and anyone who tries to get in his way.

