Featured in @{"The I in Team" LINK "IINTEAM"}.

These vermin-headed demons became the desire of Ms. Walsh. Their defense mechanism is a sharp, spear-like bone that protrudes from their hand during battle. Ms. Walsh deployed the Initiative to capture one with its arm intact so she could use it on her twisted creation, Adam.

