@{b}Queller Demon@{ub}

Appeared in @{"Listening To Fear" LINK "LISTENINGTOFEAR"}.

Summoned by Ben in order to cover-up for Glory's brain-draining activities, the Queller demon seeks out the mentally ill and kills them with what looks like lumpy shower gel.

