@node "ABOUTVAHRALL" "Buffy.guide: About Vahrall demon"

@{b}Vahrall demon@{ub}

Featured in @{"Doomed" LINK "DOOMED"}.

These talon covered demons came seconds away from opening the hellmouth under the Sunnydale High library. They performed an ancient ritual involving the Word of Valios, the bones of a child and the sacrifice of themselves. Fortunately both Buffy and Riley were there to intervene with their attempt to unleash hell on Earth.

