@node "ABOUTVERUCA" "Buffy.guide: About Veruca"

@{b}Veruca@{ub}
()

Appears in @{"Wild at Heart" LINK "WILDATHEART"}.

The lead singer of the band Shy, Veruca was a charismatic and sexy young performer who instantly drew the attention of Oz. She turned out to be an intense advanced werewolf. She drew upon Oz's animal desires and tried to lure Oz into accepting the brutal nature of his werewolf side. When it was apparent that Oz wasn't seeing things her way, she went after Willow, but Oz ripped through her jugular before she could do any harm. The experience was so profound that Oz left Sunnydale and Willow to spend some time on his own to find himself.

