@node "ABOUTZACARAY" "Buffy.guide: About Zacaray Kralik"

@{b}Zacaray Kralik@{ub}
(Jeff Corber)

Appears in @{"Helpless" LINK "HELPLESS"}.

On her 18th birthday, Buffy was forced to perform the Cruciamentum test, in which she had to fight a vampire foe without her Slayer powers. The Watcher's council chose Zack, an insane vampire who was committed to an asylum for torturing and murdering over a dozen women when he was alive, and he proved to be a little to powerful for their game.

